verbose_text: RANKL induced osteoclastogenesis is also dependent on co-stimulatory signaling through immunoreceptor tyrosine based activation motif (ITAM)-containing adaptors, Fc receptor common gamma (FcR gamma) and DNAX activating protein of 12 kDa (DAP12).
